desc_long								关于这款游戏							Boyle Wolfbane wanted to rule the world. He failed. Miserably. Forced into retirement early, Boyle now spends his days arguing with haunted trees and scaring off the occasional knight. At least he still has Fang, his loyal storm wolf. Things could be worse. He could have been born a hero.Features include a sophisticated battle and menu system. There are also many things to squash, burn, and collect. And… You. Will. Laugh. (Unless you are a zombie, in which case, we cannot help you.)FeaturesRecruit minions to aid you in your questCollect magical cheekis along your journeyOffer your skills to become part of a night watch Join a coven and expand your horizonsTransform friends into creaturesDiscover the locations and purpose of mist portals						
